---

<Layout
  title="AI-Powered Marketing for Plastic Surgery Clinics & Med Spas"
  description="Transform your aesthetic practice with AI-powered marketing. Automated SEO, patient communication, conversion-optimized websites, and paid ads‚Äîall designed to fill your consultation calendar."
  structuredData={structuredData}
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <span class="hero-label reveal">Aesthetics & Plastic Surgery</span>
        <h1 class="hero-title reveal reveal-delay-1">
          Fill your consultation calendar.
          <span class="highlight">Automatically.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2">
          Your patients are searching for procedures right now. We build the AI-powered marketing
          systems that capture their attention, nurture their interest, and book them on your
          calendar‚Äîwhile you focus on transforming lives.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">
            Grow Your Practice
            <svg
              width="16"
              height="16"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#case-study" class="btn btn-secondary">See Results</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <picture>
            <source srcset="/images/services/aesthetics-hero.webp" type="image/webp" />
            <img
              src="/images/services/aesthetics-hero.png"
              alt="AI-powered marketing dashboard for aesthetic clinics showing patient leads and consultation bookings"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </picture>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats Bar -->
    <section class="stats-bar" id="stats-section">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div class="stats-grid">
          {
            stats.map((stat, index) => (
              <div class={`stat reveal reveal-delay-${index + 1}`}>
                <span class="stat-value" data-value={stat.value}>
                  {stat.value}
                </span>
                <span class="stat-label">{stat.label}</span>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section class="problem section-padding">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div class="problem-grid">
          <div class="problem-content reveal">
            <span class="section-label">The Challenge</span>
            <h2>Your skills are exceptional. Your marketing isn't.</h2>
            <p>
              You spent years mastering your craft. You deliver results that change people's lives.
              But when it comes to marketing? Most aesthetic practices are stuck in the past‚Äîrelying
              on word-of-mouth and hoping patients find them.
            </p>
            <p>
              Meanwhile, your competition is everywhere. Patients are researching procedures online,
              comparing options, reading reviews‚Äîand booking with whoever shows up first and looks
              most trustworthy.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-list reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="problem-item">
              <span class="problem-icon">üëª</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Invisible Online</strong>
                <p>
                  Your competitors rank for "rhinoplasty near me" while your website collects dust
                  on page 3.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-item">
              <span class="problem-icon">üìâ</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Leads Falling Through</strong>
                <p>Inquiries come in but never convert. No follow-up system means lost patients.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-item">
              <span class="problem-icon">üí∏</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Wasted Ad Spend</strong>
                <p>
                  Previous agencies burned through your budget with generic campaigns and nothing to
                  show for it.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-item">
              <span class="problem-icon">‚è∞</span>
              <div>
                <strong>No Time for Marketing</strong>
                <p>
                  You're busy with patients. Marketing falls to whoever has a free moment‚Äîwhich is
                  never.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section class="solution section-padding bg-dark" id="services">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
          <span class="section-label">The Solution</span>
          <h2>AI-powered marketing that works while you sleep</h2>
          <p>
            We combine aesthetic industry expertise with AI automation to create marketing systems
            that generate consultations around the clock‚Äîwithout requiring your constant attention.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="features-grid">
          {
            services.map((service, index) => (
              <div class={`feature-card reveal reveal-delay-${(index % 3) + 1}`}>
                <span class="feature-icon">{service.icon}</span>
                <h3>{service.title}</h3>
                <p>{service.description}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Case Study Section -->
    <section class="case-study section-padding bg-gradient" id="case-study">
